@startuml Studenten-Registrierung
title Sequenzdiagramm: Studenten-Registrierung

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2

actor "Prüfungsamt" as PA
participant "Gateway\n(8080)" as Gateway
participant "User-Service\n(8081)" as User
participant "Auth-Service\n(8085)" as Auth
participant "Tenant-Service\n(8084)" as Tenant
database "User-DB" as UserDB
database "Auth-DB" as AuthDB

PA -> Gateway: POST /api/users\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>\n{firstName, lastName, email,\npassword, matrikelnummer,\nroles, tenantIds}
activate Gateway

Gateway -> Gateway: JWT validieren\nRolle = PRUEFUNGSAMT ✓

Gateway -> User: POST /api/v1/users
activate User

User -> Tenant: GET /api/v1/tenants/{id}\n(X-Service-API-Key)
activate Tenant
Tenant --> User: Tenant existiert ✓
deactivate Tenant

User -> User: Validierung:\n- Email unique\n- Matrikelnummer unique\n- Tenant existiert

User -> Auth: POST /api/v1/auth/register-credentials\n(X-Service-API-Key)\n{email, password, matrikelnummer,\nroles, tenantIds}
activate Auth
Auth -> Auth: Password hashen (BCrypt)
Auth -> AuthDB: INSERT AuthCredentials
AuthDB --> Auth: ✓
Auth --> User: 201 Created
deactivate Auth

User -> UserDB: INSERT User
UserDB --> User: User

User --> Gateway: 201 Created\n{userId, matrikelnummer, ...}
deactivate User

Gateway --> PA: 201 Created
deactivate Gateway

@enduml

